{"tid":2098844,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"譚仔三哥外賣皮蛋驚見大量蛆蟲","createTime":"2020-07-07T19:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T22:04:09.000Z","uid":49004,"like":353,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"ba6f309ea9d5e77aa01c075dc38d4371b8851b6f","tid":2098844,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T19:31:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/494795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F494795&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivR0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=c8fe8ea4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/494795</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200707/357172491677995008.jpeg/GJ5hJxkHSJsU2xt-PYYqzzyeVjR2H6_PTBqO4EwajuA?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200707%2F357172491677995008.jpeg%2FGJ5hJxkHSJsU2xt-PYYqzzyeVjR2H6_PTBqO4EwajuA%3Fv%3Dw640&h=a5b6cc52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《香港01》飲食記者向「譚仔三哥米線」（下稱「三哥」）查詢，「三哥」接到投訴後已即時向事主退款及了解，並就事件致歉。<br />\n<br />\n炎炎夏日，大家可能都會叫一碟涼拌小食消暑，但食之前記得看清楚，早前一名網民就在Facebook群組「天水圍友」上載影片，留言：「天水圍頌富譚仔三哥，買皮蛋送蛆蟲，食唔食由你哋決定。」片中見到多條蛆蟲在皮蛋表面蠕動，十分驚嚇，事主更指自己已將樣本送交食環署。「三哥」已經立即棄置該批次的皮蛋並跟進，亦就事件道歉。"},{"pid":"b291bb36b3165eb9639cb6317466accd6ecf998a","tid":2098844,"uid":134012,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T19:36:18.000Z","msg":"蛋白質"},{"pid":"85201d65894cea51d29d68e0b01e2ae37f568a47","tid":2098844,"uid":191453,"like":125,"dislike":4,"score":121,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T19:36:53.000Z","msg":"蛋白質<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a40becb5f7f6c690c67bf536ffcadd8ff288744","tid":2098844,"uid":191453,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"b291bb36b3165eb9639cb6317466accd6ecf998a","tid":2098844,"uid":134012,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T19:36:18.000Z","msg":"蛋白質"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T19:37:08.000Z","msg":"dllm"},{"pi